dct_title_s: Map of Upper Auglaize River Basin showing availability of underground water
dct_alternative_sm: Ohio water plan inventory. Underground water resources. Upper Auglaize River Basin
dct_description_sm: Map side also contains legend and explanation of map symbols.
"Prepared by ALFRED C. WALKER, Geologist, Ohio Division of Water, from data compiled by Lawrence R. Brunstetter".
Text includes information about generalized stratigraphic sequence of the rocks in the Upper Auglaize Basin and the quality of underground water.
